<h3><span class="editsection">[<a href="/w/index.php?title=Carl_Sagan&amp;action=edit&amp;section=11" title="Edit section: By Sagan">edit</a>]</span> <span class="mw-headline">By Sagan</span></h3>
<ul>
<li><i>Planets</i> (<a href="/wiki/LIFE_Science_Library" title="LIFE Science Library" class="mw-redirect">LIFE Science Library</a>), Sagan, Carl, Jonathon Norton Leonard and editors of Life, Time, Inc., 1966</li>
<li><i>Intelligent Life in the Universe</i>, <a href="/wiki/Iosif_Samuilovich_Shklovskii" title="Iosif Samuilovich Shklovskii" class="mw-redirect">I.S. Shklovskii</a> coauthor, Random House, 1966, 509 pgs</li>
<li><i>UFO's: A Scientific Debate</i>, Thornton Page coauthor, Cornell University Press, 1972, 310 pgs</li>
